{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be innovative and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Legal Group</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #003366; /* Deep Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #e6f0ff; /* Light Blue */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff;\n            --accent-color: #0059b3; /* Slightly lighter blue for accents */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.7), rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/003366/ffffff?text=Legal+Excellence') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            min-height: 600px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        #services .service-item {\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 30%;\n            margin: 20px 1.5%;\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            vertical-align: top;\n        }\n\n        #services .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        #services .service-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        #services .service-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #services .service-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n        }\n\n        #about, #contact {\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        #about .container, #contact .container {\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        #about p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.8;\n            text-align: justify;\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 15px;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            padding: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #cccccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact input::placeholder,\n        #contact textarea::placeholder {\n            color: #888888;\n        }\n\n        #contact button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 15px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            #hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            #services .service-item {\n                width: 90%;\n                margin: 20px auto;\n                display: block;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Apex Legal Group</h1>\n            <p>Your Trusted Partners in Legal Excellence</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#hero\">Home</a>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Navigating Complexities, Delivering Clarity</h2>\n            <p>We provide comprehensive legal solutions with unwavering commitment and strategic insight. Partner with us for a clear path forward.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Core Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-gavel\"></i>\n                <h3>Corporate Law</h3>\n                <p>Guiding businesses through formation, compliance, mergers, and acquisitions with precision and foresight.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-balance-scale\"></i>\n                <h3>Litigation</h3>\n                <p>Aggressively representing clients in court, advocating for their rights with expertise and determination.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-handshake\"></i>\n                <h3>Real Estate Law</h3>\n                <p>Facilitating smooth and secure property transactions, from residential closings to complex commercial developments.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-user-shield\"></i>\n                <h3>Intellectual Property</h3>\n                <p>Protecting your innovations and creative works through patents, trademarks, and copyrights.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Apex Legal Group</h2>\n            <p>Founded on the principles of integrity, expertise, and client-centered advocacy, Apex Legal Group has established itself as a premier law firm dedicated to achieving optimal outcomes. Our team of seasoned attorneys brings a wealth of experience across diverse legal fields. We believe in building strong, lasting relationships with our clients, understanding their unique needs, and providing tailored legal strategies that are both effective and efficient. We are committed to upholding the highest standards of professional conduct and to being a steadfast guide through the intricate landscape of the law.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Legal Group. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>123 Legal Lane, Suite 456, Metropolis, State 78901 | <a href=\"tel:+1234567890\">(123) 456-7890</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch shortly.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}